                        Technical Projects
                    </h1>
                    <div class="mb-2">
                        <p class="text-lg">
                            <b>In-Browser Markdown Editor</b> | <em
                                >Developer</em
                            > |
                            <a
                                href="https://markdown.chrisnowicki.io"
