                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <p class="text-lg">
                            <b>AWS S3 get-put-delete</b> | <em>Developer</em> |
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/chris-nowicki/aws-s3-get-put-delete"
                                class="text-purple-600 hover:underline"
                                target="_blank"
                                >https://github.com/chris-nowicki/aws-s3-get-put-delete</a
